OL,5, Owners of around 50,000 UK properties  
OL,6, held by foreign companies remain hidden
OL,7, from public view, despite new          
OL,8, transparency laws.                     
OL,10,FThe Register of Overseas Entities,     
OL,11,Flaunched in August 2022, was meant to  
OL,12,Freveal who ultimately owns UK property.
OL,14,FBut analysis by BBC News and           
OL,15,FTransparency International found almost
OL,16,Fhalf of firms required to declare who  
OL,17,Fis behind them failed to do so.        
OL,19,FLabour MP Margaret Hodge said the      
OL,20,Flegislation was not "fit for purpose". 
